{"tid":1701852,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"大家最近有冇皮膚敏感？","createTime":"2019-11-09T10:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T11:24:58.000Z","uid":64405,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b5d20ad6b902f479f7d6c6d03047660af58adc26","tid":1701852,"uid":64405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T10:53:25.000Z","msg":"(借朋友ac po )<br />\n<br />\n我本身係有出去行下街既和理非<br />\n<br />\n本身皮膚容易過敏<br />\n上星期頸同面開始痕同乾<br />\n諗住係轉天氣就無為意<br />\n照用返敏感時用既補濕，但情況愈來愈差<br />\n由本來既痕痕地同有d乾乾地變得嚴重<br />\n由頸痕到上臉，仲有d紅腫<br />\n乾到好似就裂、又有d痛同甩皮<br />\n所以頂唔順去左睇醫生<br />\n<br />\n以下係同醫生既對話<br />\n<br />\n醫: 你係邊頭返工？<br />\n我: 灣仔狗屋附近<br />\n（醫生個樣好似明左d野咁）<br />\n<br />\n醫: <br />\n其實依幾個月都多左本身皮膚容易過敏、經常係d重點地方出現既人嚟睇皮膚。近依1-2星期仲多左人黎睇皮膚，咩位置都有，主要係外露既位置，而情況又差不多。<br />\n<br />\n醫：<br />\n但因為無證據，做唔到d咩，所以依家只可以自己保護好自己！一切小心，切記口罩係最後先除！<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">首先除鞋、除衣物、除帽！所有野都除哂，之後洗手，先好除口罩！</span></strong><br />\n支持住！開d藥比你，記住要好好保護自己同身邊既人！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在此希望大家都留意一下有無類似情況，依家空氣污染好嚴重，出去行街除咗口罩記得做好全身保護！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e197271e014c248ff9e418e846ead125252bfd9","tid":1701852,"uid":64405,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T11:24:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HCo3TaQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHCo3TaQ.jpg&h=ae3c3e93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n皮膚出現紅腫 甩皮情況<br />\n<br />\n推 希望多啲人留意"},{"pid":"286a500d11baccf0bec96da8791f422d7b4c491c","tid":1701852,"uid":36251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T11:35:31.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d46321b1eb362416096836d9b34705ee9e6cb8","tid":1701852,"uid":21615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T11:59:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b18c1a0d14c62263b98be8ba922e809f6a139a","tid":1701852,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:01:00.000Z","msg":"有 講大話死全家"},{"pid":"ba166b4bba73b17c360ac5579ce9070c77adf575","tid":1701852,"uid":64405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T04:27:15.000Z","msg":"人手推"},{"pid":"426da8bad9e01a558fa091b408d82e0e4c5b987b","tid":1701852,"uid":95508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:38:58.000Z","msg":"我有 身邊d朋友無出街都有 會出水"},{"pid":"9b7cb78c60fe69423e4001e5f61598f20d662d34","tid":1701852,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:39:58.000Z","msg":"[文宣新方向]大肆宣揚TG健康禍害<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1718742\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1718742</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4aea56a07c8f3a9c28c1f74444d02d4110f3c099","tid":1701852,"uid":216096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:33:24.000Z","msg":"我沖完涼都痕 覺唔覺d水都好似怪怪地咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"f2fa4cb7562e2d2c3a5a91fa4988d68f0c15a01b","tid":1701852,"uid":185303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:24:58.000Z","msg":"記得記得記得類固醇唔好搽超過兩三個月 <br />\n啲西醫唔會話你知因為可以繼續睇症<br />\n唔好寧願中醫<br />\n<br />\n利申戒類固醇慘到仆街仲要有埋白內障"}]}